Can you what?

00:03:20.693 --> 00:03:22.352
Can I get a...

00:03:22.399 --> 00:03:24.176
Get what?

00:03:25.530 --> 00:03:30.112
A kiss? Something I dream of often.

00:03:30.183 --> 00:03:31.435
No problem.

00:03:33.064 --> 00:03:34.439
No problem? - No.

00:03:33.751 --> 00:03:35.751
After what you've told me...

00:03:48.652 --> 00:03:50.652
The kiss was really sweet.

00:04:01.932 --> 00:04:03.759
Good evening, Occenat Franzy, spokesperson.

00:04:04.938 --> 00:04:09.048
Good evening, I'm Osias Maxel, vice president of AAH and the Best Film Production.

00:04:09.419 --> 00:04:14.913
My name is Viana Edward Carlo, and it's been my dream since I was very little to become an actress 

00:04:15.543 --> 00:04:22.366
because my dream was to became an actress just like all the actresses I see on TV, like Angelina Jolie, Jenifer Lopez.

00:04:23.118 --> 00:04:33.440
When someone plays a role in a film, you have to get into the skin of the person you are playing, to do it well. For example Mr. Rigan gave me the part of a crazy person. 

00:04:34.973 --> 00:04:39.033
I have to get into the skin of a crazy person, for example, I sometimes see crazy people in the streets.

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:43.081
I have to get into the skin of the character I am playing in order to do it well.

